Register Page:

***User Name(text field):*** User can enter the username of their preference to create an account.

***Password(text field):*** User can set a password for their account .

Login Page:

![](data:image/jpeg;base64,)

<a name="br2"></a> 

***User Name(text field):*** User can enter the username of their account.

***Password(text field):*** User enters password for their account .

Home Page:

***Zoom In & Zoom out:*** Users can Zoom in and out of the page according to their requirement.

It is the initial home page to create a better user experience .

***Show All***: Reveals other options that come with the extension.

![](data:image/jpeg;base64,)

<a name="br3"></a> 

All these options will be discussed in detail below.

Start video:

![](data:image/jpeg;base64,)

<a name="br4"></a> 

***Start video button:*** On clicking the Start video button use will be able to record the screen.

***Dialog box:*** There will be a dialog box pop-up with options of which screen/tab user wants to

record.

***Downloads Dialog box:*** Displays the video and location where it is saved.

Increase & Decrease contrast:

***Increase Contrast:***Users can increase the contrast of the screen according to their preference.

![](data:image/jpeg;base64,)

<a name="br5"></a> 

***Decrease Contrast:***Users can decrease the contrast of the screen according to their

preference.

***Change Background color:***Users can change the background color of the screen according to

their preference.

![](data:image/jpeg;base64,)

<a name="br6"></a> 

Detox Search:

***Detox Search on:*** Users will be restricted from viewing sensitive content.

***Detox Search off:*** With option turned off there will be no restrictions.

![](data:image/jpeg;base64,)

<a name="br7"></a> 

Read Contents:

***Start Reading Aloud Button:*** Start reading the contents on the screen once enabled.

***Stop Reading Button:*** Stops reading the screen.

***Captions on the bottom:*** Displays the content being read.

Adjust Font Settings:

![](data:image/jpeg;base64,)

<a name="br8"></a> 

***Font Size:*** Users can change the size of the font.

***Font Color:*** Users can change the font color according to their preference.

***Font Style:*** Users can change the font Style(Italic) according to their preference.

***Font Weight:*** Users can change the font weight according to their preference.

Download files:

![](data:image/jpeg;base64,)

<a name="br9"></a> 

***Download File Button:*** users can download files in one step.

***Red highlighted borders:*** Users can choose from the contents that they want to download.

***Files Dialog box:*** Users can see where the downloaded files are saved.

Video Tutorials:

***Video Tutorials Button:*** Users can view tutorials if they have any difficulties in accessing the

features.

Blur ads:

***Blur ads button:*** Blurs ads and restricts unnecessary popups .

![](data:image/jpeg;base64,)

<a name="br10"></a> 

Relocate files:

***Relocate files Button:***Users can relocate files from one folder to another.

***Choose a file Button:*** Users can choose the file to relocate.

***Files Dialog Box:*** Users can choose the file and place to relocate.

Security Scans:

![](data:image/jpeg;base64,)

<a name="br11"></a> 

***Scan web Button:*** Users can scan the website to know if it secure or not.
